{"tid":2004533,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港共：區議會無權討論6.12事件 對議員強行拍門召見民政處幹部表示遺憾","createTime":"2020-05-06T13:31:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T13:53:52.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"032ad03a2429958e1d751d39fea77eae1597a913","tid":2004533,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T13:31:44.000Z","msg":"政府指中西區區議員嚴重影響民政處運作<br />\n06.05.2020 21:22<br />\n<br />\n政府發表聲明，對中西區區議員不願離開中西區民政處表示遺憾。聲明指區議員在未經中西區民政處的同意下，進入辦公範圍大聲喧嘩及拍門，職員己多次回應及勸喻離開，但議員仍拒絕，認為議員在民政處長時間逗留，嚴重影響民政處運作。發言人呼籲議員聚焦地區民生事項，政府會在互相尊重、遵守秩序和理性討論原則下，繼續與區議會合作。<br />\n<br />\n中西區區議會轄下的政制及保安事務委員會，原定下午開會，討論去年6月12日在金鐘的衝突。當區的民主派議員說，中西區民政事務處昨晚發電郵，以相關議題超越區議會職能為由，指秘書處不會提供服務，亦不會安排會議場地，所有政府人員均不會列席。一班民主派議員下午到中西區民政事務處辦公室請願。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1285629&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1285629%26csid%3D261_341&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBRyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=c379aa36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1285629&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"18d5355818e99e5a99bd7f3a4d5027a9a900bd98","tid":2004533,"uid":55089,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T13:32:41.000Z","msg":"開會都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da2565670a11e26996b4445299cfd28dad8391cf","tid":2004533,"uid":343361,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T13:35:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">公共事務<br />\n點解無權<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"caa4c72e046535d620cba8a64c06dd0457325e58","tid":2004533,"uid":68689,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T13:37:15.000Z","msg":"不如講下可以講咩"},{"pid":"da74a47f29b526a7d84742186930ce646d83f88f","tid":2004533,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T13:38:38.000Z","msg":"其實都係一票姐, 揀個冇咁臭嘅屎已經好過食屎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw黃碧雲 白頭佬快啲收皮"},{"pid":"3d88cb778a98babd266c2b81a1397079ac1af078","tid":2004533,"uid":14941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T13:45:30.000Z","msg":"區議員正<br />\n將抗爭者送入議會！"},{"pid":"67977029e5b56ab42c72eec57d8d7230c0d2c0df","tid":2004533,"uid":35870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T13:47:40.000Z","msg":"係根據邊個guideline話唔講得定點"},{"pid":"a3e25fdef07f6a79ed2c4824ba68b0b396a511a5","tid":2004533,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T13:48:23.000Z","msg":"都on撚9<br />\n<br />\n民意代表有無權幾時到政府同黨委法官講"},{"pid":"33f345e8c817653e3b438457abb2f3bc8d5b7de6","tid":2004533,"uid":159870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T13:48:48.000Z","msg":"會唔會被dq<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8110e58dad713391a30b9d233fa1e05cd775a7a5","tid":2004533,"uid":27250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T13:53:52.000Z","msg":"咁大個證據港共違反基本法"}]}